                            <comment id="13025597" author="veaven" created="Wed, 27 Apr 2011 04:16:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just checked 2.4, the issue is there.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13025644" author="veaven" created="Wed, 27 Apr 2011 07:09:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Willem, I think it also would be good to allow user to config their own Excutor. e.g. have a property for get/set Executor.&lt;/p&gt;

